{"tid":1298303,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人系放榜日一齊圍堵考評局(HKEAA)，迫佢哋就粉碎大量學生入U夢而作出公開道歉","createTime":"2019-07-09T00:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T08:30:09.000Z","uid":276872,"like":4,"dislike":156,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9fdc4d6562330d8da307a4f994177d227605d5","tid":1298303,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:04:00.000Z","msg":"考評局(HKEAA)透過出難到仆街嘅DSE題目，去粉碎歷年大量學生入U夢，令我哋本身有能力入到U都變成入唔到，被迫讀Asso/高級文憑/Ive，甚至retake，呢啲都係考評局惡行所致。<br />\n聽日放榜日，如果系因為俾考評局嘅仆街題目而受迫害/虐待，從而入唔到U，聽日一收到DSE成績，馬上一齊衝去以下地點圍堵：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8k7ePPD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8k7ePPD.jpg&h=03a8657f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果趕住去報Asso/高級文憑/Ive，你哋可以透過以上電話號碼打俾佢哋問候佢哋。<br />\n總之，我哋就要迫佢哋就自己殘暴行為、不負責任和黑心向全港學生道歉"},{"pid":"a941f25e31043a4981994f82134259c21e9dc980","tid":1298303,"uid":136467,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:05:43.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"de29e8a19c93bca8a1621363c0e546bc8843e429","tid":1298303,"uid":71081,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:08:00.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"0f1b2bc641e1e97e1e462d06c669738087e10e33","tid":1298303,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:08:27.000Z","msg":"港共成功左 由得我地和平遊行<br />\n<br />\n你地開始玩膠，即係證明你地不再憤怒，覺得好開心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298176</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"78292810364214b289bd20a09b7d4500a4fde8f5","tid":1298303,"uid":37389,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"你貼呢度無用架，貼去警察FB或者佢地啲協會啦，我諗好多藍衫會響應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc34c06ef96f0d22ce4348e0f2b5a167affe3bd2","tid":1298303,"uid":80763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:11:56.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"ba8a195caa5d6cb7b56dfb483b0236e380aa53dd","tid":1298